body:
Major refactoring, new features:
- better project stucture and class naming;
- request/reponse pattern;
- async parsing api;
- proxy support**;
- retries on failure**;

- remove try-with-resources, StandardCharsets.UTF_8 to support android < 19
- extend YoutubeVideo api to allow file naming; 
- properly close InputStream/OutputStream; 
- handle http response code != 200;
- added/refactored tests;

- allow to download live content if broadcast is already finished (resolves #12)
- fixed bug with missing contentLength (resolves #15); 
- AudioVideoFormat now extends Format, not AudioFormat
